data.description: Welcome to your all-inclusive haven with NO HOA! This 4-bed, 2-bath retreat beckons with a warm wood-burning fireplace and a generously equipped kitchen featuring ample counter space. The main bathroom has dual vanities, soaking tub and a separate walk in shower. Step into your backyard paradise, where a refreshing SALTWATER POOL awaits, complete with an exhilarating slide. This home invites you to savor every moment of comfort, convenience, and fun.
